reverse. I was told to change the Bushing on the shift rod.
I bought the complete guide for idiots, and I am unable to find this info.
in the book. I need to know if I change the busing and the coupling will
this correct my problem? The transmission seems fine it runs good in 3rd and
fourth. Also where are these bushings supposed to be, I can only find the
rubber boot looking things near the coupling. Where do these little white
plastic things go and are they easy to install?


